  pages    = {73--80},
  abstract = {Developers at Nokia recently initiated and used a product line to create and deliver mobile browser products. The developers learned that, to succeed, a software product line must be product and application driven, rather than reuse or platform driven. The experience at Nokia can serve as a case study for other organizations debating a similar transition.},
